; Coverage for amount.cc
; "Too many commas" error is thrown when a comma appears after
; no_more_commas has been set, which happens when the first comma
; was interpreted as a decimal separator in European style.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    1.000,50,25 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 7:
While parsing posting:
  Expenses:Food    1.000,50,25 EUR
                   ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
Error: Too many commas in amount
end test
